				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "6 months have passed since the Netherbrain was destroyed. Withers has orginized an evening for our heroes to come together once agrain from across the realms. \r\n\r\nGROUP_Players 11 is reservered for romance partners. Used for cine staging, but also used for checking for avatar Karlach branch who went to hell with their partner."
